<author>nzạr fạrs, nzạr fạrs</author>
<title>ạllh byḥbny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạllh byḥby ktyr qd mạ knt zgẖyr
 wlmạ ḥyạty ạlṭwylẗ byswʿ brbṭạ
 byjy ạlsẖyṭạn bḥylẗ kl ḥyạty bykẖrbṭạ
 wbyḥạwl bḥyạty yhdy wyswʿ byṣyr fy ysẖd
 yạ rby sẖw btqdrny wdạymaⁿạ btḥạmy ʿny
 mn ạlsẖryr btkẖlṣny lạ̉nw bygẖạr mny
 bdy ʿly̱ drbk syr ḥty̱ ạktr tmlk ṣyr
 ạ̹dẖạ qlby mʿ yswʿ kl ạ̹yạmy mạ bwṭạ
 kạmsẖ ạ̹ydy wmạsẖy ṭlwʿ mʿ mḥbẗ wʿbwṭạ
 wbykbr qlby nwsy wbtkẖlṣ mn ạlswsẗ</lyrics>
</song>